      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the saline rinse and it didnt do much at all, my head still hurts so bad. i know i should call the clinic but they are actually closed until monday and i really dont think i can make it through the night like this. its just one dose of the sudafed, it's not like im taking a bunch of them. would one pill really be that bad? it's just for the congestion so i can sleep",
